Elizabeth Rohr, the mother of Super Eagles Coach, Gernot Rohr, has died. She was 97. Nigeria Football Federation (NFF) broke the news on its verified Twitter handle on Thursday. The soccer federation commiserated with the German national over his loss. NFF wrote, “We commiserate with the Super Eagles Head coach, Mr. Gernot Rohr, who just lost his mother, Madam Elisabeth Rohr. “She was 97. May her soul rest in peace.” Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.